      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To authorize borrowers of loans under the William D. Ford Federal Direct Loan Program to modify the interest rate of such loans to be equal to the interest rate for such loans at the time of modification.</title>
      </item>
